examples.en: 'Sometimes a girl wants to be chased,' Amelia said.
The dogs saw him running and chased him.
He chased her barefoot across the meadow.
He chased the young hellions out of his yard.
Snatching up a knife, he chased the thief out of the house.
The policeman chased the mugger down the alley
This medal appears to have been chased by hand and not to have been struck from a die.
He chased Kevin halfway up the stairs.
Top graduates from the university are chased by major companies.
